text:
Hey, Producer.
I heard that  the new costumes have arrived...

Oh, of course.
They're in the warehouse, so I'll go get them.
Thank you, I'm really looking forward to it...!

Natsuha always seems so happy,
when new costumes arrive.

Yeah! Because wearing new costumes means
meeting a part of myself I didn't know before.
There's nothing quite as exciting as this!

I think Natsuha's mindset
is really positive and great.

Watch closely,
because I'll perfectly rock any costume...!
